  "A coastal community depends on both a fishing industry and a proposed offshore wind farm. Fishers worry the wind farm will disrupt fish habitats, while the wind farm would provide clean energy, construction jobs, and reduce carbon emissions. Environmentalists are divided. Using stakeholder analysis, which groups should the policy analyst identify and what should the analysis consider?": "",
